{"title":"人民公社好","authors":["萧三"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福大道比天高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产指标更跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万颗卫星将往天上抛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人多心齐气概豪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地连成一大片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁牛铁马都能满地跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都献宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚珠轴承只初步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机械、电气、化肥、水泥……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，多少轻重工业要大搞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化革命起高潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员都钻技术攻科学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自办红专大学中学小学校。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全民皆兵安全有担保，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平时向自然界进军战斗猛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人来时坚决把他彻底干净消灭掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都积极，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个都成多面手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农商学兵五位成一体。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少者怀来老者安，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩儿都进托儿所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人住在幸福院。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女再解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小家小户变大方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社食堂饭菜特别香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集体生活最快活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义风气新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为人人，人人都为我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家户户电灯照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邮电交通卫生文化娱乐都发达，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"试问农村哪样不如城市好？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人知识丰富身体好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"体力劳动成乐事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑力劳动结合实际更是妙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社好！公社好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家敲锣打鼓鸣鞭炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庆贺公社运动成高潮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年哲人理想很快得实现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少先烈流尽热血头颅抛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换得今天红旗到处飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换得愉快歌声达九霄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义加快建设好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义过渡能早到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社主义好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1958年9月1日）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}